---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="4-Week Essential Study Program | FM Dalton Perrine"
  description="A 12-page structured chess study program for players of all levels. Learn exactly what to study and how to study it — tactics, game analysis, endgames, openings, and more."
>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO
  ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="bg-navy relative overflow-hidden">
    <div
      aria-hidden="true"
      class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.035] pointer-events-none"
      style="background-image: repeating-conic-gradient(#fff 0% 25%, transparent 0% 50%); background-size: 72px 72px;"
    ></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 lg:py-28 text-center">
      <span class="inline-block font-inter text-gold text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-5">
        NextLevelChessCoaching.com
      </span>
      <h1 class="font-playfair text-white text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
        4-Week Essential<br />Study Program
      </h1>
      <p class="font-inter text-off-white/70 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        A scheduled, structured routine for daily chess study, built for players of <em>all levels</em>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       COVER PREVIEW
  ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="bg-white py-10">
    <div class="container-max flex justify-center">
      <img
        src="/images/essential-study-program-cover.png"
        alt="4-Week Essential Study Program — table of contents cover page"
        class="w-full max-w-sm rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200"
      />
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       INTRO
  ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="bg-off-white section-pad">
    <div class="container-max">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

        <p class="font-inter text-text-primary text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          I created this program for players of <strong>all levels</strong> to have a <strong>scheduled, structured routine</strong> for daily chess study. Throughout my 12+ years of teaching chess, I found that the majority of players don't know <em>what</em> to study, let alone <em>how</em> to study chess correctly. It is my goal to help you improve your play by providing you this essential study program.
        </p>

        <p class="font-inter text-text-primary text-lg leading-relaxed">
          The emphasis of this program is on <strong>consistency and active learning techniques</strong>. You will <strong>learn the most effective ways to study tactics, analyze your own games, learn from master-level games, improve at endgames, and work on openings</strong>.
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       WHAT'S INCLUDED
  ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="bg-white section-pad">
    <div class="container-max">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

        <h2 class="font-playfair text-navy text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">
          What's Included
        </h2>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">

          <div class="card flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="text-2xl flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">📄</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-playfair text-navy text-lg font-semibold mb-1">12 Pages Total</h3>
              <p class="font-inter text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
                A complete, thorough program you can print or reference digitally.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="text-2xl flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">💡</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-playfair text-navy text-lg font-semibold mb-1">Tips, Advice and Suggestions</h3>
              <p class="font-inter text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Specific guidance on how to do everything within the program correctly.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="text-2xl flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">🎬</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-playfair text-navy text-lg font-semibold mb-1">Videos Explaining Everything</h3>
              <p class="font-inter text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Step-by-step video walkthroughs so nothing is left to guesswork.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="text-2xl flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">📚</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-playfair text-navy text-lg font-semibold mb-1">Book Recommendations</h3>
              <p class="font-inter text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Curated reading suggestions to supplement your study.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="text-2xl flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">🔗</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-playfair text-navy text-lg font-semibold mb-1">Website Links and Resources</h3>
              <p class="font-inter text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Links to drills, statistics, databases, and other tools for every area of the program.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="text-2xl flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">📅</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-playfair text-navy text-lg font-semibold mb-1">Full Monthly Schedule</h3>
              <p class="font-inter text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
                4 full pages showing you <em>exactly</em> what to do every single day of the week.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <div class="card mt-4 flex gap-4 items-start">
          <span class="text-2xl flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">♟️</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-playfair text-navy text-lg font-semibold mb-1">The Why Behind the Program</h3>
            <p class="font-inter text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Full explanations for why the program is structured the way it is, so you understand the reasoning, not just the routine.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       BUY CTA
  ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="bg-navy section-pad">
    <div class="container-max">
      <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="font-playfair text-white text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-3">
          Get Instant Access
        </h2>
        <p class="font-inter text-off-white/70 text-base leading-relaxed mb-2">
          Purchase below and receive an instant download link.
        </p>
        <p class="font-inter text-gold text-2xl font-bold mb-8">
          $40
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://www.fatfreecartpro.com/i/z463"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="btn-gold text-base py-3 px-10 inline-block"
        >
          Buy Now
        </a>
        <p class="font-inter text-off-white/40 text-xs mt-6">
          Secure checkout via PayPal. Hope you enjoy it!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


</Layout>
